      <title>星展银行在创纪录的一年内削减了首席执行官的薪酬方案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/dbs-cuts-ceo-s-pay-package-in-record-year-marred-by-glitches</link>
      <description><![CDATA[星展集团控股有限公司 (DBS Group Holdings Ltd.) 在一年内削减了首席执行官皮尤什·古普塔 (Piyush Gupta) 的可变薪酬部分，该银行的数字服务中断，导致其创纪录的利润黯然失色。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-06/dbs-cuts-ceo-s-pay-package-in-record-year-marred-by-glitches</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 00:49:23 GMT</pubDate>
