      <title>亿万富翁马克·贝尼奥夫购买土地后向夏威夷医院捐赠 1.5 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/benioff-gives-150-million-to-hawaii-hospitals-after-buying-land</link>
